the terms of the Artistic License (see LICENSE or 
http://www.opensource.org/licenses/artistic-license.html) 

This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful,
but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of
MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.  See the Artistic
License for more details.

Requirements: 
    PHP3
    MySQL (tested with 3.23.x)
    a web-browser (doh!)

Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://blacknova.net

Credits:
    This work is based on the old BBS games that went by many names
    (Tradewars, Galactic Warzone, Yankee Trader, Ultimate Universe, and
    many other names like this) but shares no code with them.  It is
    written 100% in PHP/HTML.  
    Please refer to the DEVLIST file to see
    the current list of developers.

Installation:
    Please see the INSTALL file.

ChangeLog:
    None yet.

Documentation:
    None to speak of yet.

Enjoy,

Ron Harwood <harwoodr@blacknova.net>

